Stage 1 of 8: Your First Minutes

A short tutorial starts automatically for new characters: a guide named
Nim follows you and teaches looking, moving, gear, and safe combat.
Type "tutorial" to see your current step and "engage nim" to continue.

Learn to examine things with "xa", check your "inventory", and read
your "score". If you get lost, "ncot" returns you to the Center of
Town, where the Newbie Tome Dispenser (pull lever, read tome) holds the
town directions.

